bd$Month <- as.factor(bd$Month)
bd$Month <- factor(bd$Month, levels=c("September", "April", "June"))
bd$Treatment <- as.factor(bd$Treatment)
bd$Treatment <- factor(bd$Treatment, levels=c("N", "S", "OUT"))
